txt.en:
Bounty: Bel Inzûl Proto-crow

There is no safety while the proto-crow soars above the skies in the westernmost part of Bel Inzûl.

Slaughter the menace and return to Bel Inzûl's healer for reward.

Do not go alone.
Speak with the healer at the outpost on Bel Inzûl
You defeated the menace in the western skies. Return to the healer at the outpost on Bel Inzûl to claim your reward.
You accepted a bounty for defeating the proto-crow that soars above the western section of the island.
'The menace of the skies is no more? You want the price offered for its defeat, yes?\n\n'We thank you, friend. Killing the creature makes our efforts on the island much safer.'
You defeated the Bel Inzûl proto-crow
Gather a fellowship and make your way to the western side of Bel Inzûl. Defeat the Bel Inzûl proto-crow.
